{"tid":552853,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[分化]【流感肆虐】消息指幼園小學明起停課防爆發,點解小學中學同大學無得停~你地唔係人嗎?","createTime":"2018-02-07T02:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T03:34:31.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"faa0cdcadf5ada87080c179c538caf0d732be8bf","tid":552853,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T02:42:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180207/57802134\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180207%2F57802134&d=gcwCLdnYsGG3nWdkoZNjkCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=414e588a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180207%2F57802134&h=d8016b2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180207/57802134</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n冬季流感肆虐，逾百間學校爆發流感，特首林鄭月娥昨午與港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇，以及中大醫學院呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌會面，聽取有關疫苗注射成效、流感病理情況，並指會聽取專家意見後才可決定學校是否需要提早放農曆新年假，以減低感染情況，強調要做決定前要有科學基礎。多間傳媒引述消息指，因應流感爆發嚴重，幼稚園和小學明天起停課。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心今早10時半會舉行記者會，由總監黃加慶匯報冬季流感的最新情況。中文大學醫學院呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌、和港大醫學院微生物學系講座教授袁國勇亦會出席。"},{"pid":"7d2585c07b282ab2c75ad264a27816e2352e0bf7","tid":552853,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T02:43:01.000Z","msg":"小學有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ee590366babe5a29c6416a6425e301da43c923","tid":552853,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T02:48:11.000Z","msg":"點解要返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192d27957f69175028513f5637688584c6eac041","tid":552853,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":